          "settings": {
            "review_text": "\"As I’ve gotten older, my digestion just hasn't been the same, especially with dairy and proteins. Since I started taking Enzyme, I’ve noticed a huge improvement in how I feel after eating. I don’t deal with that uncomfortable 'stuck' feeling anymore, and I feel like I’m getting so much more out of my nutrition.\"",
