          "type": "testimonial",
          "name": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "review_text": "\"I’ve experimented with several digestive aids, but Enzyme is the first one that consistently works for me regardless of what I eat. Whether it’s a heavy cheat meal or my daily prep, it helps everything move smoothly. It’s become a staple in my gym bag and my kitchen cabinet for maintaining daily comfort.\"",
