          "name": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "review_text": "\"I never realized how much better I could feel until I started supporting my body’s natural digestion with Enzyme. I have so much more energy in the afternoons because my body isn't working overtime just to break down my lunch. It’s a simple, effective solution that has truly improved my overall quality of life.\"",
