            "review_text": "\"I used to feel incredibly sluggish and heavy after every dinner, but adding Enzyme to my routine has made a world of difference. I can tell my body is actually processing my meals better because the post-meal bloat is completely gone. It’s given me the freedom to enjoy my favorite foods without the usual discomfort.\"",
